329
00:31:24,883 --> 00:31:26,009
Kang No-eul.

330
00:31:28,511 --> 00:31:30,179
Terkonfirmasi.

331
00:31:30,179 --> 00:31:33,933
Berikut rincian penjemputan yang telah Anda atur.

332
00:31:33,933 --> 00:31:36,978
31 Oktober 2024,

333
00:31:36,978 --> 00:31:41,482
